-----------------
Uninstall Jenkins From Mac : '/Library/Application Support/Jenkins/Uninstall.command'
                              sudo rm -rf /var/root/.jenkins ~/.jenkins


sudo rm -rf /Users/Shared/Jenkins
and to delete the jenkins user and group (if you chose to use them):

sudo dscl . -delete /Users/jenkins
sudo dscl . -delete /Groups/jenkins



start Jenkins : sudo launchctl load /Library/LaunchDaemons/org.jenkins-ci.plist
stop  Jenkins : sudo launchctl unload /Library/LaunchDaemons/org.jenkins-ci.plist

Add Arguments to Jenkins ( Location of the file ) : /Library/Application Support/Jenkins/jenkins-runner.sh
----------------


Java Location : /Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines


Take a Part of the screen ctrl + shift + 4
Ctrl + alt + delete in mac Cmd + Opt + Esc


